Basic components and functionality implemented in Zend Framework using its provided example.

This is currently very basic functionality and lot of things are missing.
To see some of the code working online visti http://eagerfish.eu/projects/zfw-basic-example/public/


To setup project you have to create database and import sql file found in folder /sql. It contains users table and admin record. Also /application/configs/application.ini file must be modified to fit your environment. 


To login as admin use:
  username: admin@admin.com
  password: admin@admin.com
